description.plain:
Cico P (formerly Cicoeee P) is a 23-year-old rapper from Jacksonville, TX. With his southern swag and charisma, he tells compelling stories of family, money, relationships and life in the streets of East, TX. A former athlete, he brings that determination, hustle and work ethic into his music. His sound is gritty, yet melodic, and effortlessly blends sounds of Hip Hop and R&B. He is most known for his 2019 single that was first released in his album “Sweet Union”, Tampa which gained fame on the platform TikTok in early 2021 for its line

That boy bad news, he a menace to society
